Dialogue: 2,0:21:18.65,0:21:20.88,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,显示墓碑之形态
Dialogue: 2,0:21:21.27,0:21:21.76,Dialogue_CN_Alt,,0,0,0,,冰
