Dialogue: 2,0:21:22.04,0:21:22.80,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,狱
Dialogue: 2,0:21:26.65,0:21:28.77,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,贯穿吧 红焰
Dialogue: 2,0:21:47.30,0:21:49.67,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,八极焰剑?
Dialogue: 2,0:21:50.03,0:21:52.14,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,为什么人类能…
Dialogue: 2,0:21:53.30,0:21:54.48,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,审判完毕
Dialogue: 2,0:22:00.05,0:22:00.93,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,老头
Dialogue: 2,0:22:01.33,0:22:02.56,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,摩洛克先生
Dialogue: 2,0:22:11.52,0:22:16.02,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,拉艾露莎 你的 我们的父亲最厉害了
Dialogue: 2,0:22:18.64,0:22:19.98,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.14,0:22:21.34,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,拉艾露莎
Dialogue: 2,0:22:22.80,0:22:24.95,Dialogue_CN,,0,0,0,,愿意叫老朽父亲吗
